indimail (@version@-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * token.c (bogofilter). Clear tokens only when allocated
  * fixed recursive loop when email is sent to register-spam, register-ham, ham and spam
  * bogofilter-qfe.in - use config file and wordlist argument to bogofilter
  * fixed abormal exit in DIGEST-MD5 for non existing users
  * vchkpass - figure out domain for user for brain dead clients like MS Outlook
  * swaks - when using AUTH DIGEST-MD5, use realm from control/me
  * iwebadmin - user.c, util.c - .trivial_password sets password change to clear text
  * vmoddomain.c - display a more helpful usage option
  * vfilter.c - set PWSTRUCT for non-existent user. This will eliminate one database lookup in vdelivermail
  * smtpd.c - allow restricting of MASQUERADE to the value set by MASQUERADE env variable
  * added remoteip argument (ipv4) to spfcheck(). Fixed problem in smtpd, spfquery, parsing ipv4 mapped ipv6 addresses.
  * upgraded to clamav-0.97.4

